extraSigns.title: Welcome to Puppertown
extraSigns.description:
Population: 938 residents and 1,204 beloved pups.
Founded: 1912 as a seasonal kennel camp that blossomed into a year-round festival village.
Claim to fame: Hosts the Moonlight Muzzle Parade, where bioluminescent collars light up the central ring.
